(56, 'ACCESSIMEDECS', '<p class="aboveBulletHeadline">Access IMEDECS Portal</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Enjoy an easy, user-friendly system when it&#39;s convenient for you!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With our simple review-management-system, AccessIMEDECS, it&#39;s easy to get the information you need any time, anywhere with an Internet connection.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Through this client portal, you&#39;ll:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Save time.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:35px; margin-top:-18px;">This system is extremely easy to use. You can share information with IMEDECS in real-time, enter your case and upload documentation (including color photos) in seconds.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Maintain privacy and security.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:35px; margin-top:-18px;">AccessIMEDECS is HIPAA-compliant (Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act), ensuring that your information remains private. Access to the portal is limited to representatives with authenticated user IDs and passwords.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:35px; ">Health information is secure while the technology remains flexible to handle new policies, procedures and necessary updates.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Receive finished reports easily.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:35px; margin-top:-18px;">AccessIMEDECS is completely user-friendly. You&#39;ll receive e-mail notifications when you have uploaded a case successfully to IMEDECS or when IMEDECS uploads your report on a review.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:35px; "><em>You&#39;ll know what&#39;s&nbsp;going on at all times.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Generate instant reports.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:35px; margin-top:-18px;">AccessIMEDECS provides the ability to report on case status, service time compliance and outcomes. Plus, there is an option to export query results to an MS Excel format.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>Experience top-level customer service that combines technology and the human touch.</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The AccessIMEDECS technology makes it easy for you to get the information you need at any time. But, we are also available via phone and email to help answer your questions too!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>Ready to learn more about this easy and efficient service?</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<table style="margin-left:-12px !important;">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class="aboveBulletHeadline" style="text-align:left" valign="top" width="70%"><strong>To request a demo of AccessIMEDECS, please <a href="contact-us" style="text-decoration:underline;">click here.</a>&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: right;"><a class="button hollow primary learnMorebutton" href="contact-us" style="font-size: 18px;">LEARN MORE</a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'accessimedecs', 1, 0, 2, '', '', '', '', '', 21, '', '[null,null]', 0, '[null,null]', 0, '', 2, 0),
(57, 'State/Federal Information', '<p>The mission of IMEDECS is to provide independent, informed expert medical review services that resolve coverage disputes or evaluate the quality of care. Through its medical review program, IMEDECS is dedicated to quality healthcare and improved clinical outcomes. IMEDECS provides the following services to assist state and federal government entities in ensuring that care is necessary, timely, delivered appropriately and billed appropriately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="aboveBulletHeadline">IMEDECS Federal Services and Experience</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Department of Justice</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Department of Health and Human Services</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">U.S. Office of Personnel Management</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">U.S. Department of Veterans Affairs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p class="aboveBulletHeadline">Accreditation&#39;s and Certifications</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Accredited by URAC as a Comprehensive Independent Review Organization</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Certified as a Women-Owned Small Business (WOSB) through the U.S. Small Business Administration (SBA) program</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Certified Woman-Owned Business through WBENC (Women&rsquo;s Business Enterprise National Council)</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Woman-Owned Business state certifications from the Commonwealth of Pennsylvania and the State of Delaware</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p class="aboveBulletHeadline">IMEDECS is certified to conduct external appeals in the following states:</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%;">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td valign="top">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li class="pageList">Arizona</li>\r\n				<li class="pageList">Colorado</li>\r\n				<li class="pageList">Delaware</li>\r\n				<li class="pageList">Idaho</li>\r\n				<li class="pageList">Illinois</li>\r\n				<li class="pageList">Indiana</li>\r\n				<li class="pageList">Massachusetts</li>\r\n