(46, 'Other Services', '<p>We provide a variety of additional services and customizable solutions.</p>', 'homeservices1501484849', 1, 0, 10001, '', '', 'READ MORE', 'other-services', '_self', 6, '', '', 0, '', 0, 'fa fa-plus', 0, 0),
(75, 'Other Services', '<p class="aboveBulletHeadline">Customizable Solutions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Are you in need of a service that is not specifically identified in the current services listed?&nbsp; Then give us a call at 215-855-4633 ext. 332. Talk with us about your challenge and we will work with you to find<br class="mobileBreak2" />\r\na solution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IMEDECS prides itself on its dedication to being responsive to its client&rsquo;s needs. Over the years we have successfully customized programs and services that have allowed clients to meet specific regulations, program requirements and/or standards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Again, if you don&rsquo;t see the service that you need specifically listed here, call us. Some of our most successful services were developed in response to a client&rsquo;s need that was previously uncharted territory. We will work with you to design a complete solution that addresses your concerns.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="aboveBulletHeadline">Medical Coverage Policy Evaluations</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Health plans must develop or update the clinical decision-making policies used to approve or deny health care services. We offer an invaluable tool to assist health plans and managed care organizations during this process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IMEDECS&#39;&nbsp;actively practicing, board-certified physicians, with expertise in providing the treatment at issue, will evaluate the policy against scientific literature and current practice guidelines. This way, they can provide recommendations of additional indications, limitations or exclusions, coding changes (if necessary), and additional citations relevant to the policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="aboveBulletHeadline">With IMEDECS&#39;&nbsp;Medical Coverage Policy Evaluations, you:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Receive Best Practices.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:35px; margin-top:-18px;">Current, clinical practice guidelines developed by relevant professional societies, government organizations, healthcare organizations, or medical specialty organizations are considered and referenced as part of the reviewers&rsquo; evaluations.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Obtain the Best Evidence.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:35px; margin-top:-18px;">The expert reviewers research late-phase clinical trials or well-designed studies to gather the best evidence regarding the diagnosis or treatment at issue.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Discover the Best Solutions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:35px; margin-top:-18px;">Your reports will include answers to your questions like:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class="pageListInner"><em>Do you believe the policy to be accurate as written?</em></li>\r\n	<li class="pageListInner"><em>Do you believe the conditions listed as criteria for coverage to be complete?</em></li>\r\n	<li class="pageListInner"><em>Are there any FDA-approved uses missing? If so, describe the diagnosis and suggest what the community standard is for treatment.</em></li>\r\n	<li class="pageListInner"><em>Where does the procedure fall in the hierarchy of available treatment options?</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>To see a sample MCPE report, </strong><a href="http://www.imedecs.com/sample-app/view_file.php?id=4"><strong>click here</strong></a><strong>.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="aboveBulletHeadline">Disability Reviews</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IMEDECS&#39;&nbsp;Disability Reviews assist disability claims managers and employers in the management of their short and long-term disability claims. By utilizing IMEDECS for your disability reviews, you will receive an accurate decision in the timeframe you require.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Each review is performed by a specialty-matched, board-certified physician that is engaged in<br class="mobileBreak1" />\r\nactive practice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And your reviews can:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Assess the source of the illness or injury;</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Evaluate the appropriateness of the course of treatment and return to work potential; and</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Provide claimants with information related to their benefits.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>With IMEDECS&#39;&nbsp;Disability Review Services, you receive an accurate decision in the timeframe you require.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>To see a sample Disability Report, </strong><a href="http://www.imedecs.com/sample-app/view_file.php?id=4"><strong>click here</strong></a><strong>.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<table style="margin-left:-12px !important;">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class="aboveBulletHeadline" style="text-align:left" valign="top"><strong>For more information, please contact us here.&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n			<td style="text-align: right;"><a class="button hollow primary learnMorebutton" href="contact-us" style="font-size: 18px;">LEARN MORE</a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'other-services', 1, 0, 12, '', '', '', '', '', 8, '', '[null,null]', 0, '[null,null]', 0, '', 2, 0);
