(77, 'Reviewer Opportunities', '<p class="aboveBulletHeadline">Join our expert review panel and voice your opinion!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At IMEDECS, we continually seek the best qualified physicians, CPC, attorneys, medical experts, and more to participate on our well-known, Independent Review Panel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As an Independent Review Organization, we conduct medical record reviews of treatments that have been denied by health insurance companies as experimental/investigational or not medically necessary.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We also conduct peer reviews to ensure that services are being provided in accordance with recognized standards of care. And we review health plan coverage policy to ensure that it is accurate and consistent with current practices and the scientific literature.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="aboveBulletHeadline">Why Conduct Reviews for IMEDECS?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to being paid for your time, as a part of our Medical Review Panel, you can:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="pageList">\r\n	<li class="pageList">Lend an informed, objective voice to the review of coverage decisions;</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Provide recommendations for improving the quality of care;</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Help shape health plan coverage policy to be consistent with the literature and current standards of practice; and</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Stay abreast of the care being provided by one&#39;s peers and more!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Most important, you can reach our customer service team when necessary.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We respect your time and value your work on our Medical Review Panel. Because of this, we provide the best customer service possible to help you through the process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unlike many others, we are available to answer your questions and provide the personal attention<br class="mobileBreak1" />\r\nyou deserve.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="aboveBulletHeadline">Ready to Find Out More?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To be considered for IMEDECS&#39;&nbsp;Medical Review Panel, you must be board certified, hold a current, non-restricted license in a state of the United States and be actively engaged in the practice of medicine. All panel members are credentialed in accordance with URAC standards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Upon successful credentialing, expert reviewers are &quot;recruited&quot; on a case-by-case basis to ensure availability, experience with the issue in question, and to screen for potential conflicts of interest.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once assigned to a case review, the expert reviewer is expected to render an accurate, objective decision based on the facts of the case, scientific evidence and national or health plan criteria (as appropriate) in a timely manner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IMEDECS is currently seeking reviewers in the following specialties:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="pageList">\r\n	<li class="pageList">Addiction Psychiatry</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Adult Bone Marrow Transplant</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Adult Orthopedics</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Allergy and Immunology</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Child Psychiatry</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Clinical Genetics</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Gastroenterology</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Infectious disease</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Medical Oncology</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Neurosurgery</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Oral Maxillofacial</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Pediatric Bone Marrow Transplant</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Pediatric Endocrinology</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Pediatric Orthopedics</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Pediatric Physical Medicine and Rehabilitation</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Pediatric Urology</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Plastic Surgery</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Podiatry</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Psychiatry (all disciplines)</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Pulmonology</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Surgical Oncology</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Surgical Transplant (Liver, Kidney , pancreas)</li>\r\n	<li class="pageList">Vascular</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>If you are interested, please fill out this </strong><a href="http://imedecs.exceedcms.com/reviewer-form"><strong>Reviewer Form</strong></a><strong> and click &quot;Submit.&quot; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Thanks so much for your time! We will be in touch and look forward to speaking to you!</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table align="left" style="margin-left:-10px;">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="text-align: left;"><a class="button hollow primary learnMorebutton" href="contact-us" style="font-size: 18px;">LEARN MORE</a></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'reviewer-opportunities', 1, 0, 4, '', '', '', '', '', 30, '', '[null,null]', 0, '[null,null]', 0, '', 2, 0),
