('home-paragraph-contents-welcome2', '<p><img alt="" src="http://imedecs.tk/images/imadecs-logo-b.png" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As one of the first companies accredited when the standards were written (around 1998 as Hayes Plus), Independent Medical Expert Consulting Services, Inc. (IMEDECS) has a long history of providing the highest quality medical review products&hellip; backed by unmatched customer service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you are a C-level executive, healthcare provider, individual, part of a procurement/purchasing department, or another facilitator, you will receive expert information relevant to your specific needs, deadlines and regulatory specifications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And because top experts in numerous, medical areas come to IMEDECS for exciting and unique review opportunities, we offer a physician panel with unsurpassed quality, depth and breadth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With IMEDECS, you&rsquo;ll also enjoy talking to a real human being who can answer your questions. And if it&rsquo;s after business hours, the AccessIMEDECS cutting-edge online review management system is accessible <strong>twenty-four hours a day, seven days a week</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="big"><em>Are you ready to get the specialty reviewers and accurate and comprehensive responses you need on time&hellip; without stress?</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Check out our various services, join our newsletter, and feel free to contact us with your questions.<br />\r\nThanks so much, and we look forward to serving you soon!</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="action top"><a class="button hollow primary" href="contact-us">LEARN MORE</a></div>\r\n'),
